{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1857585, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 364345, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有借必有贷，借贷必相等", "timestamp": 1623748798, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1857626, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 364345, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "时域卷积频域相乘", "timestamp": 1623749111, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1857639, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 364345, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Pikaqiu～", "timestamp": 1623749242, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1857649, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 364345, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "毁灭吧，我累了", "timestamp": 1623749328, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1857660, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 364345, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "自动化是万金油", "timestamp": 1623749426, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1857705, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 364345, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "凡可列的，皆可编码为01序列，所谓计算就是从一种编码到另一种编码的可操作的映射；取一条无限长纸带，划成无数个空格子，将输入编码写在纸带上，用手指着最左端的格子，把脑子复位到初始状态，心中默念转移函数，然后修改当前格的数字、移动手指、改变大脑状态；这机器可能进入接受态或拒绝态停机，也可能永不停机，唤之曰图灵机；这机器本身也有编码，通用图灵机可以从编码模拟它的运行；这机器是至高的、最终的，凡其他模型可以计算的，它也都能计算。", "timestamp": 1623749871, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1857768, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 364345, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "可以用电压的高低表示01，这01运算就能实现所有算法！", "timestamp": 1623750522, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1857822, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 364345, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "转行", "timestamp": 1623751107, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1857843, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 364345, "